    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. Given how much the city is pushing for these kinds of green initiatives, it seems like a pretty straightforward way to hit those climate goals. Are there any major hurdles or disagreements that actually slow down projects like this?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
